<item>
            <title>[ENTESB-2496] CXF deadlocks at org.apache.cxf.bus.extension.ExtensionManagerImpl.getBeansOfType</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/ENTESB-2496</link>
                <project id="12314570" key="ENTESB">JBoss Fuse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems CXF and Spring causes a deadlock on org.apache.cxf.bus.extension.ExtensionManagerImpl.getBeansOfType().&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks that the original Spring issue, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8471&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8471&lt;/a&gt;, was fixed on Spring 3.2 so I assume this was fixed for Fuse 6.1 since it uses 3.2.8.RELEASE.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This Spring bug report also points to a CXF issue that, after digging on the Internet, I could find this: &lt;a href=&quot;http://mail-archives.apache.org/mod_mbox/cxf-users/201311.mbox/%3CA0BA72E3-9696-45EE-BA2D-916F76420769@apache.org%3E&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://mail-archives.apache.org/mod_mbox/cxf-users/201311.mbox/%3CA0BA72E3-9696-45EE-BA2D-916F76420769@apache.org%3E&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems was indeed a CXF issue fixed on the 3.x branch.. This is the fix: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cxf/commit/b03c1404c39f53fb1a590671ff02db04b1c45403&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cxf/commit/b03c1404c39f53fb1a590671ff02db04b1c45403&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is there a way to get this backported to Fuse 6.1?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Maven 3.2.3 on Windows 7 (64 bit), with Java 1.7.0u72 (64 bit)&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
